item.title: I don't need some features, can I disable them?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Sure, you don't need to use any of the included features. Just deactivate the specific plugin or switch it off in the customizer.

item.title: Is there an online user documentation?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Yes there is. It is available at http://inventorwp.com/documentation/ and we do our best to keep our online documentation always up to date.

item.title: Can I define my own fields?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Yes of course. You can do it either using our field mnanager or you can follow our guide for developers in our online documentation.

item.title: Is it difficult to build content like in this demo?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: You don't need to build it from scratch. You can use our One-Click installation tool to import whole demo content.

item.title: Are there any hidden fees?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Absolutely not. All features are included in the plugins bundled inside. You don't need to pay for any extra third party plugins.
